{
  "_about": "Real label photos for OCR eval, spanning clean front-of-label shots (beer/wine/spirits) through wildly-colorful RTDs and deliberately-bad captures. NOT representative COLA submissions (the product targets pre-market COLA review of clean manufacturer label artwork, modelled by the synthetic golden corpus, tests/corpus); this set stress-tests real OCR on real artwork and confirms graceful degradation. Each image is committed under tests/eval/images/ (see images/ATTRIBUTION.md for source + licence). ground_truth is the COLA fields a human would file; expect is the stable outcome (quality grade, brand verdict bucket, ABV recoverability).",
